body_html:
I have confirmed that if I only use quantize_weights , the pb model can run on Android, but can not detect anything.
But I can use rounded_weights to transform the pb model , and the final apk size compressed about 17M !

So I think the issue can be closed!

body:
I have confirmed that if I only use quantize_weights , the pb model can run on Android, but can not detect anything.
But I can use rounded_weights to transform the pb model , and the final apk size compressed about 17M !

So I think the issue can be closed!
